fm: int longestPalindrome(string s)      {         vector<int>Map(256,0);         for (int i=0; i<s.size(); i++)             Map[s[i]]++;                  int sum=0;         int flag=0;         for (auto a:Map)         {             if ((a % 2) ==1)             {                 sum+=a-1;                 flag=1;             }             else                 sum+=a;         }                  return sum+flag;              }

fm: int numberOfArithmeticSlices(vector<int>& A)      {         int n = A.size();         unordered_map<long,int>dp[1000];         int count = 0;                  for (int i=1; i<A.size(); i++)         {             for (int j=i-1; j>=0; j--)             {                 long diff = (long)A[i]-(long)A[j];                 count += dp[j][diff];                                  if (dp[j].find(diff)!=dp[j].end())                     dp[i][diff] += dp[j][diff]+1;                                                     else                     dp[i][diff] = 1;             }         }                              return count;     }

fm: int numberOfBoomerangs(vector<pair<int, int>>& points)      {         int result=0;         for (int i=0; i<points.size(); i++)         {             unordered_map<int,int>Map;             for (int j=0; j<points.size(); j++)             {                 int dis= (points[i].first-points[j].first)*(points[i].first-points[j].first)+(points[i].second-points[j].second)*(points[i].second-points[j].second);                 Map[dis]++;             }             for (auto a:Map)             {                 result+=a.second*(a.second-1);             }                     }                  return result;              }

fm: int findMaxLength(vector<int>& nums)      {         unordered_map<int,int>Map; // presum -> j         Map[0] = -1;                  int ret = 0;         int presum = 0;         for (int i=0; i<nums.size(); i++)         {             if (nums[i]==1)                 presum += 1;             else                 presum -= 1;                          if (Map.find(presum)!=Map.end())                 ret = max(ret, i - Map[presum]);             else                 Map[presum] = i;         }                  return ret;     }

fm: int findPairs(vector<int>& nums, int k)      {         if (k<0) return 0;         unordered_set<int>Set;         unordered_set<int>minSet;                  for (int i=0; i<nums.size(); i++)         {             if (Set.find(nums[i]-k)!=Set.end())                 minSet.insert(nums[i]-k);             if (Set.find(nums[i]+k)!=Set.end())                 minSet.insert(nums[i]);             Set.insert(nums[i]);         }                  return minSet.size();             }

fm: int findPairs(vector<int>& nums, int k)      {         sort(nums.begin(),nums.end());                  int i=0;         int j=1;         int result=0;                  while (j<nums.size())         {             while (nums[j]<nums[i]+k) j++;             if (nums[j]==nums[i]+k)                 result++;             i++;             while (i<nums.size() && nums[i]==nums[i-1]) i++;             j=max(j,i+1);         }                  return result;     }
